    "body" : "<p>The question itself has already been addressed above. \nJust adding part of the default values.</p>\n\n<p>As per <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/cd/E13150_01/jrockit_jvm/jrockit/jrdocs/refman/optionX.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://docs.oracle.com/cd/E13150_01/jrockit_jvm/jrockit/jrdocs/refman/optionX.html</a></p>\n\n<p>The default value of Xmx will depend on platform and amount of memory available in the system.</p>\n"
