    "question_id" : 14763079,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>-Xms</strong> is the initial heap size for the startup, however, during the working process, the heap size can be less than <strong>-Xms</strong>  due to users' inactivity or GC iterations.\nThis is not a minimum required heap size.</p>\n<p><strong>-Xmx</strong> is the maximum heap size</p>\n"
